"Field Tasking Manager (Field-TM) ń ran àwọn ẹgbẹ́ lọ́wọ́ láti fi ìmọ̀ "
"agbègbè kún àwọn ẹ̀yà maapu nípasẹ̀ ìṣọ̀kan iṣẹ́ maapu ní pápá."

#: app/templates/landing.html:592
msgid ""
"Field-TM facilitates collaborative mapping by supporting and extending "
"mature tools\n"
"        like ODK and QField. It is a standalone mobile and web workflow "
"that helps teams collect\n"
"        geospatial data efficiently with commonly available Android "
"devices."
msgstr ""
"Field-TM ń jẹ́ kí iṣẹ́ maapu àjọṣe rọrùn nípasẹ̀ títì lẹ́yìn àti fífi "
"agbára kún àwọn irinṣẹ́ tó ti dàgbà bí ODK àti QField. Ó jẹ́ ìlànà iṣẹ́ "
"alágbèéká àti wẹẹbù olómìnira tí ń ran àwọn ẹgbẹ́ lọ́wọ́ láti kó data "
"àyè-ìbùdó jọ ní ìmúṣẹ́ tó dára pẹ̀lú àwọn ẹ̀rọ Android tí ó rọrùn láti "
"rí."

#: app/templates/landing.html:599
msgid "A project manager demonstrates FieldTM mapping workflow on a laptop"
msgstr "Alákóso iṣẹ́ kan ń fi ìlànà iṣẹ́ maapu FieldTM hàn lórí kọ̀ǹpútà alágbèéká"

#: app/templates/landing.html:605
msgid "Main Features"
msgstr "Àwọn àǹfààní pàtàkì"

#: app/templates/landing.html:608
msgid "Flexible Data Collection"
msgstr "Ìkó data tó rọrùn láti yí padà"

#: app/templates/landing.html:610
msgid ""
"Support diverse survey forms, multiple data formats, and adaptable "
"workflows that\n"
"          fit different operational needs."
msgstr ""
"Ó ń ṣètìlẹ́yìn fún oríṣìíríṣìí fọ́ọ̀mù ìwádìí, ọ̀pọ̀lọpọ̀ ọ̀nà data, àti "
"àwọn ìlànà iṣẹ́ tó lè yí padà láti bá onírúurú àìní iṣiṣẹ́ mu."

#: app/templates/landing.html:615
msgid "Open Source and Customizable"
msgstr "Orísun ṣíṣi àti ètò tí a lè ṣe sí ìfẹ́"

#: app/templates/landing.html:617
msgid ""
"Adapt Field-TM to your own survey logic, data structures, and integration"
"\n"
"          requirements."
msgstr ""
"Ṣe Field-TM sí ìfẹ́ rẹ gẹ́gẹ́ bí ọgbọ́n ìwádìí rẹ, àkópọ̀ data, àti "
"ìbéèrè ìṣọ̀kan."

#: app/templates/landing.html:622
msgid "Entity-Level Tracking"
msgstr "Ìtẹ̀lé ní ipele nkan"

#: app/templates/landing.html:624
msgid ""
"Monitor survey progress at task and feature level so managers can make "
"informed\n"
"          decisions quickly."
msgstr ""
"Máa tọ́pasẹ̀ ìlọsíwájú ìwádìí ní ipele iṣẹ́ àti ẹ̀yà kí àwọn alákóso lè "
"ṣe ìpinnu tó dá lórí ìmọ̀ ní kíákíá."

#: app/templates/landing.html:632
msgid "Who is it for?"
msgstr "Ta ni ó jẹ́ fún?"

#: app/templates/landing.html:635
msgid "Project Manager"
msgstr "Alákóso iṣẹ́"

#: app/templates/landing.html:636
msgid "Create and coordinate field campaigns"
msgstr "Dá ìpolongo pápá sílẹ̀ kí o sì ṣọ̀kan wọn"

#: app/templates/landing.html:638
msgid ""
"Project managers use Field-TM to set up mapping projects, define areas of"
" interest,\n"
"          design survey forms, and split work into manageable tasks."
msgstr ""
"Àwọn alákóso iṣẹ́ máa n lo Field-TM láti ṣètò iṣẹ́ maapu, ṣàlàyé àwọn "
"agbègbè ìfẹ́, dá fọ́ọ̀mù ìwádìí sílẹ̀, kí wọ́n sì pín iṣẹ́ sí àwọn iṣẹ́ "
"kéékèèké tó rọrùn láti ṣakoso."

#: app/templates/landing.html:642
msgid "Define a project area and upload or choose a survey form"
msgstr "Ṣàlàyé agbègbè iṣẹ́ kí o sì gbe fọ́ọ̀mù ìwádìí sókè tàbí yan ọkan"

#: app/templates/landing.html:643
msgid "Split the area into tasks and generate a data extract"
msgstr "Pín agbègbè náà sí iṣẹ́ kí o sì dá ìyọkúrò data sílẹ̀"

#: app/templates/landing.html:644
msgid "Publish the project to ODK Central or QFieldCloud"
msgstr "Tẹ iṣẹ́ náà jáde sí ODK Central tàbí QFieldCloud"

#: app/templates/landing.html:645
msgid "Share a QR code so mappers can start collecting data"
msgstr "Pín kóòdù QR kan kí àwọn olùṣe maapu lè bẹ̀rẹ̀ sí í kó data jọ"

#: app/templates/landing.html:649
msgid "Field Mapper"
msgstr "Olùṣe maapu pápá"

#: app/templates/landing.html:650
msgid "Collect data in the field with your phone"
msgstr "Kó data jọ ní pápá pẹ̀lú fóònù rẹ"

#: app/templates/landing.html:652
msgid ""
"Mappers do not need to log in to Field-TM. Once a project manager "
"publishes a\n"
"          project, mappers access it directly in their mobile app of "
"choice."
msgstr ""
"Àwọn olùṣe maapu kò nílò láti wọlé sí Field-TM. Ní kete tí alákóso iṣẹ́ "
"bá ti tẹ iṣẹ́ kan jáde, àwọn olùṣe maapu máa lè wọlé sí i taara nínú ohun"
" èlò alágbèéká tí wọ́n bá yàn."

#: app/templates/landing.html:656
msgid "Scan the QR code shared by your project manager"
msgstr "Ṣe skani kóòdù QR tí alákóso iṣẹ́ rẹ pín"

#: app/templates/landing.html:657
msgid "The project loads automatically in ODK Collect or QField"
msgstr "Iṣẹ́ náà máa ṣíra rẹ̀ lọ́fàá ní ODK Collect tàbí QField"

#: app/templates/landing.html:658
msgid "Navigate to your assigned task area and collect data"
msgstr "Lọ sí agbègbè iṣẹ́ tí a yàn fún ọ kí o sì kó data jọ"

#: app/templates/landing.html:659
msgid "Submit your survey, which goes straight to the server"
msgstr "Fìdí ìwádìí rẹ múlẹ̀, èyí tí yóò lọ taara sí olupin"

#: app/templates/landing.html:666
msgid "Field-TM Use Cases"
msgstr "Àwọn ọ̀nà lílò Field-TM"

#: app/templates/landing.html:671
msgid "Field mapping in progress"
msgstr "Iṣẹ́ maapu pápá ń lọ lọwọ"

#: app/templates/landing.html:676
msgid "1. Community Mapping"
msgstr "1. Maapu àwùjọ"

#: app/templates/landing.html:678
msgid ""
"Field Tasking Manager empowers communities to map informal settlements, "
"public\n"
"            facilities, and local services for inclusive planning."
msgstr ""
"Field Tasking Manager ń fún àwọn àwùjọ ní agbára láti ṣe maapu àwọn "
"ibùgbé àìlétò, àwọn ilé ìṣèjọba gbogbo ènìyàn, àti iṣẹ́ agbègbè fún ìṣètò"
" tó kó gbogbo ènìyàn sí i."

#: app/templates/landing.html:683
msgid "2. Urban Planning and Management"
msgstr "2. Ìṣètò àti ìṣàkóso ìlú"

#: app/templates/landing.html:685
msgid ""
"Build smarter cities with coordinated surveys of houses, roads, and "
"utilities\n"
"            through clear, manageable mapping tasks."
msgstr ""
"Kọ́ àwọn ìlú ọlọ́gbọ́n sí i pẹ̀lú ìwádìí ilé, ọ̀nà, àti àwọn amáyédẹrùn "
"tó wà ní ìṣọ̀kan nípasẹ̀ àwọn iṣẹ́ maapu tó ṣòro díẹ̀ láti ṣakoso."

#: app/templates/landing.html:690
msgid "3. Disaster Response and Recovery"
msgstr "3. Ìdáhùn sí àjálù àti ìmúpadàbọ̀sípò"

#: app/templates/landing.html:692
msgid ""
"Rapidly map damaged infrastructure after disasters, coordinate "
"volunteers, and\n"
"            deliver reliable data for relief operations."
msgstr ""
"Ṣe maapu àwọn amáyédẹrùn tí wọ́n bajẹ́ lẹ́yìn àjálù ní kíákíá, ṣọ̀kan "
"àwọn olùfẹ̀yàrá, kí o sì pèsè data tó gbẹ́kẹ̀lé fún àwọn iṣẹ́ ìrànwọ́."

#: app/templates/landing.html:701
msgid "Resources"
msgstr "Àwọn orísun"

#: app/templates/landing.html:709
msgid "Data Prep"
msgstr "Ìmúra data"

#: app/templates/landing.html:710
msgid "HOT Export Tool"
msgstr "Irinṣẹ́ fífi data jáde HOT"

#: app/templates/landing.html:712
msgid "Download task-ready geospatial data extracts for your project area."
msgstr ""
"Ṣe igbasilẹ àwọn ìyọkúrò data àyè-ìbùdó tó ti ṣetan fún iṣẹ́ fún agbègbè "
"iṣẹ́ rẹ."

#: app/templates/landing.html:721 app/templates/landing.html:733
msgid "Documentation"
msgstr "Ìwé àlàyé"

#: app/templates/landing.html:722
msgid "ODK Central Guide"
msgstr "Ìtọ́sọ́nà ODK Central"

#: app/templates/landing.html:724
msgid "Learn how to manage forms, app users, and field submissions in ODK."
msgstr ""
"Kọ́ bí a ṣe ń ṣakoso fọ́ọ̀mù, àwọn olumulo ohun èlò, àti àwọn fífiṣẹ́ "
"pápá nínú ODK."

#: app/templates/landing.html:734
msgid "QField Guide"
msgstr "Ìtọ́sọ́nà QField"

#: app/templates/landing.html:736
msgid "Set up QFieldCloud projects and mobile workflows for offline mapping."
msgstr ""
"Ṣètò àwọn iṣẹ́ QFieldCloud àti àwọn ìlànà iṣẹ́ alágbèéká fún iṣẹ́ maapu "
"àìsí ìkànnì."

#: app/templates/landing.html:746
msgid "Need assistance?"
msgstr "Ṣé o nílò ìrànlọ́wọ́?"

